description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 65, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 130, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, Box for South, and Leverage for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10652-11460-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [130 Votes, Top 15% Score]
